briefdescription.para: This type is a polling structure that handles the properties of "watched" or "guarded" DisplayType items (e.g., Questions, Sections). The properties handled include, e.g., ActivateIf/Deactivate, VisibleIf/InVisibleIf, EnabledIf/DisabledIf. The type allows the creation of simple conditions that control the property value of the watched item.
